{"title":"Help Kickstart the New Incredible Multitools by Daysaver","link":"https://bikerumor.com/new-incredible-bike-multitools-by-daysaver/","date":1686063401000,"content":"<p>Straight outta Zurich, Switzerland, the people that brought us the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/a-45-gram-nine-function-multi-tool-the-pb-swiss-made-daysaver-is-super-light-compact/\" target=\"_blank\">Daysaver</a> are at it again. This time, with two new <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/daysaver/daysaver-incredible-the-completely-adaptive-multitool?ref=discovery&amp;term=daysaver\" target=\"_blank\">multitool concepts</a>, one dubbed the Daysaver Incredible Multitool, the other, the Incredible Tubeless. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup-800x352.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool closeup\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup-800x352.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup-297x131.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup-120x53.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup-768x338.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-closeup.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Daysaver</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage-800x338.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool open bit storage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage-800x338.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage-297x125.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage-120x51.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage-768x324.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-open-bit-storage.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Incredible touts being fully customizable claiming that “<em>not only can bits be combined exactly as needed. Bikers can also take it with them in the way they prefer. Whether in the bike, on the bike, in the pants/jersey pocket, or in the backpack – the choice is yours</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"501\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool with and without insert\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert-297x116.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert-800x313.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert-120x47.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-with-abd-without-insert-768x301.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Incredible Multitool with insert sleeve (right) and Incredible Tubeless Tool (left)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out their <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/daysaver/daysaver-incredible-the-completely-adaptive-multitool?ref=discovery&amp;term=daysaver\">Kickstarter here</a>. the Incredible Multitool is available now with special deals. And if you’re quick you can get over 30% off. It looks like you can get both the Incredible Multitool, Incredible Tubeless Tool, and 2 handlebar mounts for a pledge of $139.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Shipping will be global and deliveries are predicted to start Jan 2024. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-high-and-low-torque.jpeg\"><img width=\"680\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-high-and-low-torque.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool high and low torque\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-high-and-low-torque.jpeg 680w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-high-and-low-torque-297x148.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-high-and-low-torque-120x60.jpeg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The concept of the Incredible Multitool is that it has the advantages of an Allen wrench, being able to reach all of the screws on your bike while offering two different levers to apply the right amount of torque. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"361\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage-800x361.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool bit storage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage-800x361.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage-297x134.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage-120x54.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage-768x346.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-bit-storage.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the same time, the spring-loaded and lockable levers are foldable making the tool easy to store in indiscreet, out-of-the-way areas on your bike. There’s also integrated bit storage, using a sliding, magnetic mechanism that opens and closes allowing for quick and easy access… with or without gloves.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits-800x200.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool mix match bits\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits-800x200.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits-297x74.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits-120x30.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits-768x192.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-mix-match-bits.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Mix and Match bits for ultimate customization</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The MixMatch bits, allow you to customize the bits that you take with you on your ride. Using a proprietary lock interface, the bits can be combined allowing you to bring only the tools you need without bringing the unnecessary. The stainless, hardened steel bits are also available for sale separately as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Incredible Tubeless Tool/Chain Breaker</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image.png\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"326\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image.png\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-297x121.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-120x49.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-768x313.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Incredible Tubeless tool is another offering that is designed to provide a quick and convenient solution for tubeless tire repair. The tubeless tool is designed so that the plug is already equipped with the plugs while being stowed in the handlebar, making it immediately ready for use. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"306\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use-800x306.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool chain breaker in use\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use-800x306.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use-297x113.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use-120x46.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use-768x293.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-chain-breaker-in-use.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It uses an aluminum design for durability even when being used with force, important to consider when fixing a broken chain using the tool’s patented chain guide. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"451\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-800x451.jpeg\" alt=\"Daysaver Incredible Multitool tubeless tool close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-800x451.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-768x433.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-400x225.jpeg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up-1200x675.jpeg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Daysaver-Incredible-Multitool-tubeless-tool-close-up.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To top off the tubeless tool, you’ll find a handy, included blade to remove the protruding plug ends. The blade actually looks large enough to partake in preparing some trailside charcuterie…</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a few different options to store the Incredible Multitool on your bike. The handlebar mount expands to match the inside diameter of your handlebar with a set screw. Removal is easy with the clever quick-release system. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Features </h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Incredible Multitool</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Hardened stainless steel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Approx. 60 gram</li>\n\n\n\n<li>96.5 x 14.5 mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bits included: HEX 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5, 6, 8 (integrated in the tool), T25. Additional bits T10, T15, T20, T30, Plus (JIS), can be purchased</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>IncredibleTubeless tool</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>6061 T6 aluminum</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hardened stainless steel, fiberglass reinforced polyamide</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Approx. 40 grams</li>\n\n\n\n<li>99x16mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Includes chain breaker, blade, tubeless plug</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Incredible Mount</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>6061 T6 aluminum, fiberglass reinforced polyamide</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Approx. 8 grams</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Handlebar end: diameter 26 mm, 2.5 mm thick. For handlebars with inner diameter 17-21mm</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://daysaver.fun/en-int\" target=\"_blank\">DaySaver.fun</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-incredible-bike-multitools-by-daysaver/\">Help Kickstart the New Incredible Multitools by Daysaver</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bf99bf36e2e105224aec6025bac2746d835aa92ce820dd9699683bce5188251e","category":"Cycling"}